\f1 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Vacuum Nylon Packaging Bags are high-performance industrial packaging solutions designed to provide excellent vacuum sealing, moisture resistance, puncture resistance, and product protection for sensitive electronic and industrial applications.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Manufactured using durable multilayer nylon materials, these bags offer strong barrier performance and are widely used in Semiconductor Packaging, PCB Packaging, electronic components, food packaging, and precision industrial products requiring vacuum protection during storage and transportation.\
